ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2012-1 (Nekaneet)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT, No. 2012-1 (NEKANEET) in order to add the name of the Nekaneet, the name of its governing body and the description of the lands where the Nekaneet First Nations goods and services tax law could apply.
